data.description: Bring your animals and your toys!! Four bedroom and 2.75 bath home located on 5.10 acres outside of Lyman. Home has been tastefully updated inside and out! Property includes a detached, oversized, 2 car garage as well as a separate detached 1 car garage with hay storage. Perfectly set up and ready for animals/livestock. Corrals and pasture are partitioned for easy pasturing, loading and shelter with water on site. Home has the convenience of being attached to city water, but also has 2 separate,private wells for watering. Cozy Gazebo with a fire pit that is set up for movie nights, as well as an additional living quarters that also has 4 bedrooms, 2 baths and 1792 Sq Ft of living space. Newer metal roofs on additional living quarters as well as the garage. Property also comes complete with solar panels to ease those electric bills!!! This is a must-see property if you are looking for country living. Call Bobbi Dolezal, 307-747-5059 to schedule a showing.
